ad| encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Iranica |year=1988 |accessdate=2007-11-08 |url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/baqer-abu-jafar-mohammad|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia |last=Madelung |first=Wilferd | title=Hasan ibn Ali | encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Iranica | year=2003 |accessdate=2015-03-11|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/hasan-b-ali|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia|last=Madelung |first=Wilferd | title=\u1e24osayn B.\u02bfAli. Life and Significance in Shi'ism | encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Iranica | date=2004|accessdate=2015-03-11 |url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/hosayn-b-ali-i|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia | encyclopedia = Encyclopedia of the Modern Middle East and North Africa | last =Mattar | first =Philip | year = 2004 | publisher = Macmillan Reference USA | isbn = 978-0-02-865772-1|ref=harv}} \n* {{cite encyclopedia|last=Nasr |first=Seyyed Hossein | authorlink=Seyyed Hossein Nasr | title=Muhammad | encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica Online | year=2006 |accessdate=2015-03-11|publisher= Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica, Inc. |url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9105853/Muhammad|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia|last=Nasr |first=Seyyed Hossein | title=Ali | encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica Online | year=2007|accessdate=2015-03-11|url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9005712/Ali|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia |last=Poonawala |first=I. K. |authorlink= | title=\u02bfAli B. Abi \u1e6caleb | encyclopedia=Encyclop\u00e6dia Iranica | accessdate=2014-07-07|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/ali-b-abi-taleb|year=1985|ref=harv}}\n\n; Books\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Amir-Moezzi|first=Mohammad Ali|title=The Divine Guide in Early Shi'ism: The Sources of Esotericism in Islam|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4g6Od9f1rFAC&pg=PA115|date= 1994|publisher=SUNY Press|isbn=978-0-7914-2122-2}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Amir-Moezzi|first=Mohammad Ali|title=The Spirituality of Shi'i Islam: Belief and Practices|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZadmgNbs91sC&pg=PA206|date= 2011|publisher=I. B. Tauris|isbn=978-1-84511-738-2}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Ansariyan |first1=Hussein |title=Ahl Al-Bayt The Celestial Beings on the Earth |date=2007 |publisher=Ansariyan Publications |ref=harv |isbn=978-964-438-873-6 |url=http://www.maaref-foundation.com/english/library/pro_ahl/general/ahl_al-bayt/ |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006183739/http://www.maaref-foundation.com/english/library/pro_ahl/general/ahl_al-bayt/ |archivedate=October 6, 2014 }}\n* {{cite book|last=Chittick|first=William C.|authorlink=|title=A Shi'ite Anthology|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rMnFZOHkurcC&pg=PA138|accessdate=27 April 2015|year=1980|pages=136\u2013140|publisher=SUNY Press|isbn=978-0-87395-510-2|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last =Corbin|first =Henry |authorlink = Henry Corbin|title = History of Islamic Philosophy|publisher = Kegan Paul International in association with Islamic Publications for The Institute of Ismaili Studies |year = 1993|isbn = 978-0-7103-0416-2|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book | last=Dabashi | first=Hamid | authorlink=Hamid Dabashi | title= Theology of Discontent: The Ideological Foundation of the Islamic Revolution in Iran|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sTFdNNQP4ewC | publisher=Transaction Publishers | year=2006 | isbn=1-4128-0516-3|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Donaldson|first=Dwight M.|title=The Shi'ite Religion: A History of Islam in Persia and Irak|year=1933|publisher=Burleigh Press|isbn=978-0-404-18959-4 }}\n* {{cite book|last=Dungersi|first=Mohammed Raza|title=A Brief Biography of Hazrat Fatima (s.a.)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6dJSAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA1|publisher=Bilal Muslim Mission of Tanzania|year=1994|oclc=66915718|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv |last=Dungersi |first=Mohammed Raza |title=A Brief Biography of Imam Hasan al-Askari |year=2005 |url=http://www.maaref-foundation.com/english/index.htm |publisher=Ansariyan Pu